



---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Experience from "../components/ExperienceCard.astro";
---

<Layout title="Experience - Amna Rafi">
  <main>
    <div class="page-hero scroll-reveal">
      <h1 class="page-title">Experience</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">
        I enjoy being part of collaborative environments where ideas flow freely, and everyone contributes to building meaningful products. Transparency, adaptability, and open communication are values I deeply appreciate, as they foster creativity, teamwork, and impactful outcomes.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline">
    <Experience
      title="Web Development Intern at Web3gle, Lahore"
      description="Collaborated with a dynamic team to build modern web solutions, strengthening teamwork and project alignment. Gained hands-on web development experience and industry insights through real-world project contributions."
      subtitle="June 2024 – August 2024"
      image="/images/web3gle.jpeg"
    />

    <Experience
      title="Product Design Intern at The Essential Studios, Islamabad"
      description="I was involved in the entire design cycle of digital products including user experience and interface design as well as visual consistency. I worked closely with cross-functional teams to create intuitive, user-focused solutions that align with the brand’s vision while maintaining both functionality and aesthetics."
      subtitle="June 2024 – August 2024"
      image="/images/essential_studio.jpeg"
    />

    <Experience
      title="Web Development Intern at CodeAlpha"
      description="It offered practical experience and greatly enhanced my comprehension of fundamental web technologies. The position focused on hands-on application, enabling me to develop real-world projects while acquiring new frameworks and honing current abilities in MERN stack. This opportunity not only enhanced my technical skills but also refined my problem-solving capabilities and equipped me to make valuable contributions to upcoming development teams."
      subtitle="May 2024 – August 2024"
      image="/images/code_alpha.jpeg"
    />
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    background: var(--accent-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    max-width: 70ch;
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .timeline {
    padding-left: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>